\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fref%3Dexternal%26v%3D2010202932561818&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=b48461d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?ref=external&amp;v=2010202932561818</a><br />\n<br />\n華利園<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t地區：荃灣芙蓉山<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t產品：桃花<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t安排：直接聯絡農夫、農場直接銷售<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t聯絡： 華利園 合時桃花 （建議fb message）<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t種植桃花六十幾年，老農退休後農二代不希望荒廢農地毅然投身其中成為職業與志業，一棵一棵努力種植，靠自己雙手努力銷售。<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hamlets.land/videos/694527001231665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhamlets.land%2Fvideos%2F694527001231665%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7YMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=b24a7857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hamlets.land/videos/694527001231665/</a>"}]}